296
00:42:51,410 --> 00:42:53,930
l won't do it anywhere else.

297
00:42:59,210 --> 00:43:01,390
Why in here?

298
00:43:07,480 --> 00:43:09,860
It must be in here,

299
00:43:12,610 --> 00:43:15,580
