<i>Projection No 58,
"Late Spring" by Yasujiro Ozu.</i>

362
01:03:53,410 --> 01:03:54,900
<i>"The Searchers" by John Ford.</i>

363
01:03:54,970 --> 01:03:56,610
<i>A masterpiece.</i>

364
01:03:56,710 --> 01:03:59,000
