I'm biding 51,000!

484
01:19:40,190 --> 01:19:41,160
More!

485
01:20:16,630 --> 01:20:19,150
I'm alive! I'm alive, damn it!

486
01:20:19,240 --> 01:20:22,690
I'm alive!

487
01:20:29,830 --> 01:20:31,340
I need money!

488
01:20:34,970 --> 01:20:37,180
Hit me, hit me!

489
01:22:15,620 --> 01:22:17,810
