514
01:32:23,870 --> 01:32:25,420
<i>Shall we begin?</i>

515
01:32:25,600 --> 01:32:27,160
<i>I've kept you waiting.</i>

516
01:32:27,320 --> 01:32:29,000
<i>This way, please.</i>

517
01:32:35,130 --> 01:32:38,310
<i>Shuji-sama wants 100 punches.</i>

518
01:32:38,510 --> 01:32:41,290
<i>Bet on how many he'll be able to stand.</i>

519
01:32:51,200 --> 01:32:53,660
